Type: Package
Package: biohelpers
Title: Convenience Functions for Biological Data Processing
Version: 0.0.0.5
Authors@R: 
    person("Xiang", "LI", , "lixiang117423@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a comprehensive suite of convenience
    functions for biological data analysis and visualization. It includes
    tools for multivariate analysis (PCA, PCoA, RDA, sPLS-DA, OPLS-DA),
    statistical testing (ANOVA with post-hoc tests, correlation analysis,
    linear regression, PERMANOVA), differential analysis (DESeq2-based
    differential expression and abundance analysis, LEfSe), data
    preprocessing (rarefaction, outlier detection, heatmap reordering),
    genomics visualization (Manhattan plots, volcano plots), microbiome
    analysis (taxonomic composition, diversity analysis), metabolomics
    workflows, and publication-ready plotting themes. The package
    standardizes complex analytical workflows across omics data types and
    provides consistent, publication-quality visualization outputs with
    minimal code requirements.
